dmca.title: TV DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google: Android Market

works.description:
2Do is one the most popular
iPhone/Symbian  
todo app on the market. The 'Getting Things Done' app found on the Google 

Android Market  
(https://market.android.com/details?id=org.freedom.ooze.android.gtd&feature=search_result)
 
has infringed our copyrights by stealing our app logo.

2Do is currently under development for Android and has been for over a  
year. We will be releasing 2Do for Android hopefully in a month or two.

We did not give permission to the HelloWorld development team to use our  
logo in any way or form. We request that they immediately withdraw their  
application until the infringement has ceased.
